title: 142: The ALDI Haul Episode (April ‘21 Edition)
itunes:title: The ALDI Haul Episode (April ‘21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie try a whopping 15 finds from ALDI! Finds like Hawaiian chicken, chicken sausage, protein wraps, a killer tzatziki dip, pb&j bites, half sour pickles, an almond-milk latte, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the find of possibly the entire year (so far)… dill pickle hummus that’s the BEST Lisa has ever had! So stop everything and push play now. Don’t forget to head on over to our Foodcast page for a list products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: It’s our BIGGEST ALDI HAULDI EVER!
